For any explanation about ABT graph coloring algorithm, please refer to
../10.1.1.29.2945.pdf & ../bessiere03a.pdf. You may find good things
like ABT graph coloring algorithm, explanation about nogood and explana-
tion about agentview. You can also take a look on my internship report
located on "../.." .

########################################################################
#######                           SRC                            #######
########################################################################

This rep contains source code.

First, you can check flowchart.eps. It is a flowchart that show briefly
how each part of code works.

Each file is documented. You can find inside how to run it.

########################################################################
#######                          TEST                            #######
########################################################################

This rep contains script that run source code itself.

for example, you can run : $ ./get_picture_async.sh
It will use all of other script and run 50 times ABT graph coloring 
algorithm on asynchronous mode. More, it store results in "result.txt"
file. Take a look at this script first in order to understand how this
script set works.

